results.name: A079848(n) - A062294(n).
comment: A079848 is the sequence of smallest primes such that the pairwise sums of not necessarily distinct elements are all distinct, whereas A062294 is the sequence of smallest primes such that the pairwise sums of distinct elements are all distinct.
link: Klaus Brockhaus, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..3600
